CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

June 6, 2014

[Cite as 06/06/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-2424.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2008-0822. Columbus Bar Assn. v. DiAlbert.

On application for reinstatement of John Eugene DiAlbert, Attorney Registration No. 0030101. Application granted and respondent is reinstated to the practice of law in Ohio, with a two-year monitored probation.
